description:
THIS REPOSITORY IS DEPRECATED AND WAS ARCHIVED (READ-ONLY) on June 19, 2020.

WISDEM has moved to a single, integrated repository at https://github.com/wisdem/wisdem

JacketSE is a systems engineering model for 3 and 4-legged lattice structures (jackets) supporting tubular steel towers for offshore wind turbines. A module for static hydrodynamic, aerodynamic, and structural design and analysis of wind turbine jacket and towers within the Systems Engineering toolbox.
name: JacketSE [SWR-14-23]
